She then decides to get a divorce as she realizes she has misspent her youth on her husband. Tsz-fung, So Chak-kei (Raymond Cho), Tong Yan (Edwin Siu) and Choi See-ki (Harriet Yeung) are amicable partners.

programme.title: The Awakening Story

Unfortunately, KI and LAM have already developed a relationship.

This spy film is loosely inspired by the James Bond movies.

programme.desc: Wong Yang is a famous martial artist who is forced to teach kung fu to the Mong Clan, an evil clan which is trying to destroy its nemesis, the Chow Clan. programme.desc: A 17-year old schoolgirl marries her 35-year-old teacher. Comedy ensues when they attempt to keep their relationship a secret despite being in the same school. programme.title: Shaolin Hand Lock
programme.desc: Li Cheng Yings father was set up and killed by his old friend Ling Hao. Li, who has learnt "Shaolin Hand Lock" from his father, is on a mission to avenge his death. He works as an undercover guard at Lings house where he meets his long-lost brother, and the two team up to take revenge for their father against Ling.

programme.title: Whose Baby is in the Classroom?
programme.desc: Chen, a male teacher in an all girls high school, is stuck with a baby that isnt his and must take care of it. As he lives on the school grounds, the baby is a source of constant distraction and worry! Luckily, his class warms to the baby and helps him take care of it while he works his charm on Li Ching, an uptight teacher in the same school.

programme.title: Vengeance Of A Snow Girl
programme.desc: A crippled woman seeks vengeance against the four men who killed her parents. However, when she crosses path with a young warrior who falls in love with her, trouble ensues as his father is one of the killers responsible for her familys massacre years ago.

programme.title: Hong Kong Rhapsody

programme.title: Tales of a Eunuch
programme.desc: Tales Of A Eunuch reunites the potent mix of martial arts superstar Gordon Liu, who plays Emperor in cognito Kang Hsi, with the kung-fu comedienne Wang Yu, an anti-Ching revolutionary. It is a film laced with wild barrages of excellent martial arts chiefly choreographed by Yuen Hua and Yuan Pien; Jackie Chans long-time kung-fu classmates. At one time, Wang was considered to be the next Alexander Fu Sheng.

programme.title: Lets Fall In Love
programme.desc: Da Yung, the son of a rich entrepreneur, meets Lian Lian, the niece of a kindergarten principal by chance. They get into a misunderstanding at the first meeting, causing Da Yung to lose his wallet. Further misunderstanding occurs when he tries to use her to act as his fiance, in order to drive away two women whom he does not like...

programme.title: The Lady Hermit

The Black Knights days are numbered when the Lady Hermit and her protege perfect the technique to take him down.

programme.title: Scandal

programme.title: Woman of the Night
programme.desc: The movie offers three stories of love and obsession. In the first tale, a young student with a voyeuristic habit spies on two of his female roommates. programme.title: The Silver Fox

programme.title: The Conmen In Vegas
programme.desc: In this sequel, King and his buddy Skinny Dragon become great partners after defeating Ma Gau Wan. As they have swindled a lot of money from an underground casino, the casino boss hunts them down and holds Skinny Dragon captive. King would need to complete an impossible task in Las Vegas in order to save Skinny Dragon.

programme.title: Tiger on Beat
programme.desc: Lazy police veteran Francis, teams up with police rookie Michael to investigate the murder of a heroin trafficker. They track down a bar girl Donna and learn that she is the sister of the dead trafficker who is killed by the drug boss. Donna decides to work with the police and the duo set up traps to arrest the drug boss based on her information.

programme.title: The Adventurers
programme.desc: Andys parents were killed by their sworn brother, Ray, when he was a child. He vows to take revenge and grows up to be a pilot. When Andy hooks up with Rays mistress, he is being hunted by Ray and flees to the US, where he ends up saving Rays daughter by chance and falling in love with her. How would Andy choose between revenge and love?

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Ma Wing Jing and his brother arrive in Shanghai to make their fortune. Befriending a powerful mobster Tam, Ma is given his nightclub when he saves Tams life. Mas fortune rises but he must overcome the corruption and violence to survive.

programme.title: Hong Kong Playboys
programme.desc: Sheng is a rich playboy who lives a carefree and fun life with the ladies, until his mother decides that he should get married. Up against other lady killers in his quest to find Miss Right, Sheng must decide what he wants.

programme.title: Project A
programme.desc: In the 19th century, the Hong Kong Marine Force fails to fight against the rampant activities of pirates and smugglers. Marine Officer Ma is determined to battle a ruthless band of pirates to regain control of the dangerous waters.

programme.title: Cherie
programme.desc: Cherie Chung plays the title character in this sexy romance as a fitness instructor who attracts the attentions of a wealthy businessman and a handsome photographer.

programme.title: Maybe Its Love
programme.desc: A girl Marble witnesses a murder case and reports it to the police. After much investigation, the police can only sort out the complicated relationships between a rich merchants mistress, a postman, a shop owner and his wife, but find no clue as to who the murderer is. Therefore, Marble decides to carry out her own investigation...

programme.title: God of Gamblers Return
programme.desc: The God of Gamblers, Gao Jin, quits gambling and live a quiet life with his wife. However, a Taiwanese crime boss wants to become the new God of Gamblers and get rid of him, so he kills Gao Jins pregnant wife to force him to the casino table. Gao Jin is indignant and vows to fight the crime boss to avenge his wifes death.

programme.title: The Eye
programme.desc: Mun undergoes a cornea transplant to correct her blindness, but ends up gaining more than the gift of sight. She shockingly realises that she is seeing another woman instead of herself whenever she looks into a mirror. Recalling that things changed ever since her cornea was replaced, Mun vows to uncover the truth behind her strange vision...

programme.title: As Tears Go By
programme.desc: Mobsters Wah and Fly are buddies. Wah loves his cousin, but cannot make their relationship work as he is a mobster. Fly infuriates a mob boss one day and got beaten up badly, implicating Wah too. He then takes up a fatal task to make amends...

programme.title: One Nite in Mongkok
programme.desc: A mainland hitman Loy is hired to avenge the death of a gangsters son but the police are onto him from the start. While hiding in the dense streets of Mongkok, Loy saves a call girl Dan Dan from some gangsters. Loy and Dan Dan are hunted around Mongkok by police and gangsters. Who wiIl find them first, the lawful force or the lawless one?

programme.title: My Dream Girl
programme.desc: Tycoon Cheung is back in China after being abroad for five years and finds his long-lost daughter, Ling, in a poor village. To transform his unrefined and dirty daughter into a lady, Cheung hires Joe as Lings image consultant.

programme.title: Days of Being Wild
programme.desc: Yuddy is an orphan who is callous towards any women who falls for him. One day, Yuddy sets out on a fateful journey to Philippines to meet with his mother, but the trip ended up disheartening him again.

programme.desc: One of the greatest fighters of all time, Boxing Hall of Famer Roberto Duran, continues his comeback against Worcester, Massachusetts native Sean Fitzgerald. He would get more than he bargained for against the young undefeated Fitzgerald, who gave Duran a more competitive fight than anyone could have expected.

programme.title: The Awakening Story
programme.desc: LAM HO SHU (WANG MING CHUN, LIZA) had fallen into a coma after a traffic accident sixteen years ago. She wakes up suddenly. With support from her husband, KI (LAU CHUNG YAN, DAMIAN), her daughters, KA (CHEUNG HO YEE, MAGGIE) and YAN (YEUNG YI, TAVIA), her son, CHAI (TANG KIN WANG, PATRICK), and best friend, LAM (SO YUK WAH, LOUISA), she takes up the responsibility of being a mother and a wife again. Unfortunately, KI and LAM have already developed a relationship.

programme.title: Virtues of Harmony
programme.desc: A widow CHI (SIT KA YIN, NANCY) owns a popular restaurant, Honey Cave, in Resonance Town. She has triplets - two boys, NIN and YUE and a daughter, YAT. NIN used to be working as a government official in the capital, but he has offended a princess and has been demoted and sent back to his hometown.

programme.title: Lives of Omission
programme.desc: LEUNG SIU-TONG (Tse Tin Wah) joins the police force again to train up undercover cops for the Criminal Intelligence Bureau. He gets to know triad member SO SING-PAK (Bosco Wong) and becomes very good friends with him. PAK is not only smart guy also calculating. He agrees to work as TONGs informer only because he sees TONG as a stepping-stone to the role of gang leader. His girlfriend, YIU HO-HO (Kate Tsui), is a barrister.

programme.title: The Family Link
programme.desc: Many people say that housewives are good-for-nothing and will only idle away their time on boring chores. But MUNG KA-KA (TANG SHUI MAN, SHEREN), TING MUI-HEUNG (YIP TUNG, CECILIA) and CHO MEI-NGO (SHEUNG TIN NGOR, KIKI) will prove them wrong. Contrary to what you might think, being a housewife is as stressful as fighting in the battlefield. The never-ending housework and the persistent family conflicts will put them on the alert at all times.

programme.title: Beauty And The Boss
programme.desc: Wong Lai-mei (Ali Lee) rejoins the workforce after playing the role of housewife for ten years after her marriage. She is employed by PR agency boss Mak Tsz-fung (Moses Chan). She then decides to get a divorce as she realizes she has misspent her youth on her husband. Tsz-fung, So Chak-kei (Raymond Cho), Tong Yan (Edwin Siu) and Choi See-ki (Harriet Yeung) are amicable partners.
